articles.author: Shyam Vasudevan
articles.title: Asian Olympic Qualifiers: Vinesh Phogat returns as Indians wrestle for Olympic quotas - ESPN India
articles.description: This is the penultimate chance for India's wrestlers to qualify for the Olympic Games, with the World Qualifiers in May being the final opportunity.
articles.content:
India's wrestlers will resume their quest for an Olympic quota over the next three days at the Asian Olympic Qualifiers in Bishkek, Kyrgyzstan.
